plot: In my very first documentary ever, I was lucky enough to sit down with Veteran, Frank Gann, and talk to him about his time in the military, the experiments he was involved with, and how one clerk at a VA cost him a whole lot.
title: Veterans UnAffairs: The Frank Gann Story
